      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "あら、過去の\n『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』の記事ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ an article…\n…from Miracle☆Idol Birthday!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4839657861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_51_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "『アイドルの願いごとを叶える誕生日企画』だって\n芽衣も渚も好き放題やらせてもらったみたいだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a \"Birthday Project to Grant Idols' Wishes\".\nMei and Nagisa seem to have gotten whatever they wanted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8666624545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
